      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 07:26:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于中国和美国经济持续疲软，保乐力加销售额下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/pernod-ricard-sales-drop-as-china-and-us-weakness-persists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保乐力加公司 (Pernod Ricard SA) 公布最新季度销售额低于预期，原因是其主要市场中国和美国的需求持续低迷，且消费者不愿花费巨资购买昂贵的酒水。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/pernod-ricard-sales-drop-as-china-and-us-weakness-persists</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 05:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ABB 上调利润率预期，因电力部门受益于数据业务繁荣</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/abb-raises-margin-outlook-as-power-unit-gains-from-data-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[ABB 有限公司上调了利润率预期，因为对数据中心的大规模投资刺激了其电网业务的需求，有助于抵消工厂自动化产品销售疲软的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/abb-raises-margin-outlook-as-power-unit-gains-from-data-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 05:04:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
