    <item>
      <title>铁矿石价格跌破 100 美元，因中国需求情绪恶化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/iron-ore-slumps-toward-100-after-housing-briefing-in-beijing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铁矿石价格跌至三周来的最低点，表明投资者怀疑中国最近的房地产市场支撑措施是否足以刺激建筑活动和钢铁需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/iron-ore-slumps-toward-100-after-housing-briefing-in-beijing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 03:55:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着刺激措施希望消退，中国股市陷入调整</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/chinese-stocks-rise-with-all-eyes-on-housing-ministry-briefing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在又一次备受期待的政策发布会未能提供投资者所希望的那种促增长刺激措施后，中国股市陷入回调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/chinese-stocks-rise-with-all-eyes-on-housing-ministry-briefing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 01:47:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
